query:
INSERT INTO application (
            job_listing_id,
            stage,
            applied_date,
            application_notes
        )
        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
        RETURNING
            id AS "id!: i64",
            job_listing_id,
            stage AS "stage: Stage",
            applied_date AS "applied_date!: NaiveDate",
            application_notes,
            created_at AS "created_at!: NaiveDateTime",
            updated_at AS "updated_at!: NaiveDateTime"
